00:02:38.760 --> 00:02:42.030 align:middle line:84%
>> One fun exercise when you're
trying to figure out what to do

00:02:42.030 --> 00:02:46.350 align:middle line:84%
is to get a big poster board
sheet of paper or a couple

00:02:46.350 --> 00:02:51.800 align:middle line:84%
of them and some colorful,
bright-colored markers.

00:02:51.800 --> 00:02:54.630 align:middle line:84%
So in the center of your poster
board what you want to do

00:02:54.630 --> 00:02:58.290 align:middle line:84%
is write out either the
question or just the topic

00:02:58.290 --> 00:03:01.540 align:middle line:84%
of what it is that you're
considering and then circle it.

00:03:01.540 --> 00:03:03.930 align:middle line:84%
And then write
everything that comes

00:03:03.930 --> 00:03:06.690 align:middle line:84%
to mind with all
the different colors

00:03:06.690 --> 00:03:08.560 align:middle line:84%
and do it as
quickly as you want.

00:03:08.560 --> 00:03:10.560 align:middle line:84%
You can draw little
pictures, whatever it is.

00:03:10.560 --> 00:03:14.370 align:middle line:84%
Write as many things that
come to your mind about this.

00:03:14.370 --> 00:03:19.050 align:middle line:84%
And then the thing to do is
to step back and just see

00:03:19.050 --> 00:03:20.880 align:middle line:90%
what you've created.

00:03:20.880 --> 00:03:24.110 align:middle line:84%
You can pin it up on a
wall for a couple of days.

00:03:24.110 --> 00:03:26.520 align:middle line:84%
And what you'll begin to
notice is that certain colors

00:03:26.520 --> 00:03:28.080 align:middle line:90%
start to pop out to you.

00:03:28.080 --> 00:03:32.070 align:middle line:84%
You think, oh, wow, I
never even thought of that.

00:03:32.070 --> 00:03:34.710 align:middle line:84%
Or certain things that
you just knew for sure

00:03:34.710 --> 00:03:37.950 align:middle line:84%
you were going to do with
this question or the situation

00:03:37.950 --> 00:03:41.780 align:middle line:84%
all of a sudden, maybe
they're not so bold anymore.

00:03:41.780 --> 00:03:45.390 align:middle line:84%
And what it does it allows
your subconscious mind

00:03:45.390 --> 00:03:50.130 align:middle line:84%
to start to create new ways of
understanding your situation.

00:03:50.130 --> 00:03:54.690 align:middle line:84%
