information inside of you.

00:03:54.690 --> 00:03:57.750 align:middle line:84%
In your body, you
have everything

00:03:57.750 --> 00:04:02.750 align:middle line:84%
you need to get the best
answer for your life.

00:04:02.750 --> 00:04:06.030 align:middle line:84%
And this is another way
that you can discover it.

00:04:06.030 --> 00:04:09.100 align:middle line:84%
>> Another way you can start to
