00:07:50.470 --> 00:07:55.140 align:middle line:84%
>> There's four different levels
to the interchange experience.

00:07:55.140 --> 00:07:58.080 align:middle line:84%
And the first level is
where you don't even

00:07:58.080 --> 00:08:01.060 align:middle line:84%
know that you don't know
that there's a problem.

00:08:01.060 --> 00:08:04.530 align:middle line:84%
