sitting around on the couch,

00:08:04.530 --> 00:08:07.680 align:middle line:84%
and you're drinking
your 12th beer.

00:08:07.680 --> 00:08:13.770 align:middle line:84%
And you're watching your
fourth rerun of some show.

00:08:13.770 --> 00:08:17.880 align:middle line:84%
And you don't even know
that there's an issue.

00:08:17.880 --> 00:08:20.730 align:middle line:84%
