there's an issue.

00:08:24.000 --> 00:08:28.170 align:middle line:84%
The second level
of interchange is

00:08:28.170 --> 00:08:30.810 align:middle line:84%
where you know that
there's something wrong,

00:08:30.810 --> 00:08:32.669 align:middle line:90%
but you don't know what it is.

00:08:32.669 --> 00:08:35.010 align:middle line:84%
And it's like there's
something there on the surface,

00:08:35.010 --> 00:08:37.750 align:middle line:84%
and you're just not feeling
right, and it's bothering you.

00:08:37.750 --> 00:08:41.669 align:middle line:84%
But you just don't
know what it is.

00:08:41.669 --> 00:08:45.280 align:middle line:84%
And it's like an itch
that you want to scratch,

00:08:45.280 --> 00:08:49.110 align:middle line:84%
