something wrong,

00:08:59.320 --> 00:09:02.340 align:middle line:84%
and you actually
know what it is.

00:09:02.340 --> 00:09:04.920 align:middle line:90%
But you don't know what to do.

00:09:04.920 --> 00:09:08.670 align:middle line:84%
