the life that you want.

00:09:30.270 --> 00:09:33.930 align:middle line:84%
The best way to turbocharge
out of that third place

00:09:33.930 --> 00:09:36.150 align:middle line:84%
is to begin to work
on your inner self

00:09:36.150 --> 00:09:39.630 align:middle line:84%
and to work on your
inner development.

00:09:39.630 --> 00:09:42.360 align:middle line:84%
>> I actually started to see
